    metaTitle: "Botox for Men Who Public Speak — Stage Presence, Confidence & Cameras",
    description: "Public speakers, keynote presenters, and men who regularly perform on camera or on stage have a heightened case for Botox. Here's why appearance matters in speaking contexts and how to optimize without losing expressiveness.",
